description:
Modify newInitCmd to support global .floop initialization.

Changes:
- Add flag: --global (initialize ~/.floop/ instead of ./.floop/)
- When --global is set:
  * Call store.EnsureGlobalFloopDir()
  * Get globalPath from store.GlobalFloopPath()
  * Create manifest.yaml in globalPath
  * Output success message with global path
- Maintain existing local initialization as default

Pattern:
  globalInit, _ := cmd.Flags().GetBool("global")
  if globalInit {
      if err := store.EnsureGlobalFloopDir(); err \!= nil {
          return fmt.Errorf("failed to initialize global directory: %w", err)
      }
      globalPath, _ := store.GlobalFloopPath()
      // Create manifest in globalPath
  }

Estimated: 30 minutes
File: cmd/floop/main.go (lines ~75-120)
